11:42.693 --> 11:45.945
<i>but also found several
intriguing artifacts,</i>

11:46.029 --> 11:48.281
including a leather strap

11:48.365 --> 11:49.708
and a gold-plated button.

11:50.701 --> 11:53.545
- I'll try over here.
- Okay.

11:53.704 --> 11:56.873
<i>However, due to the new
island-wide restrictions</i>

11:56.957 --> 11:58.383
<i>imposed by the Department</i>

11:58.542 --> 12:00.960
<i>of Community, Culture
and Heritage,</i>

12:01.053 --> 12:03.555
<i>they will need to recover
more compelling evidence</i>

